'''''Şcoala Moldovenească''''' ({{lang-en|The Moldovan School}}) was a magazine from [[Chişinău]], [[Bessarabia]], founded in May 1917 by [[Onisifor Ghibu]]. It was the successor of ''[[Cuvânt moldovenesc (magazine)|Cuvânt moldovenesc]]''<ref>[http://www.hasdeu.md/ro/ebibl/poslednij.pdf PRESA BASARABEANĂ de la începuturi pînă în anul 1957. Catalog]</ref>
